<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>VT 365 Diesel Engine - 2004 Model Year - MANIFOLDS AND EXHAUST GAS RECIRCULATION (EGR) - Installation -
        Intake Manifold and EGR Cooler
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="s26503.4.2" svcproctype="install" graphiccount="8">
        <title>Intake Manifold and EGR Cooler</title>
        <figure id="f2650332" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd06/D0653.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Front module seal</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install a new front module seal between the intake manifold and front cover module.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650333" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd14/D1422.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Intake manifold gasket with centering tab</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position a new intake manifold gasket on each side of intake manifold and run two bolts
                through each side to hold gaskets. Make sure centering tabs are facing up in the manifold, while
                positioned inboard toward the engine valley.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove protective magnetic covers from cylinder head intake ports.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650334" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd14/D1440A.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Intake manifold and EGR cooler assembly</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position intake manifold on cylinder heads.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650316" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figD14/D1458.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Dog point bolts and stud bolts</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Bolt (M6 x 95 dog point) (11)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Bolt (M6 x 95) stud (5)</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Loosely install 11 dog point bolts and 5 stud bolts.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650335" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd14/D1423A.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="432px"
                     scalefitheight="532px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Torque sequence for intake manifold mounting bolts</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Torque dog point bolts and stud bolts to the special torque value .</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650337" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd14/D1437.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Heat shield mounting nuts (right side)</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If equipped, install intake heat shield and two M6 nuts on right side of intake manifold and
                tighten to the special torque .
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650338" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd05/D0511A.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>EGR coolant inlet coupling alignment (unlocked position)</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">EGR coolant supply port cover mark</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Recess</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Single index mark</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Flat edge representing duel index marks</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect the EGR coolant inlet coupling by aligning the single index mark (if visible) or
                recess on the end of the coupling with index feature on the oil cooler cover .
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650339" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd14/D1444.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>EGR coolant inlet coupling to coolant supply port</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Index feature on oil cooler cover</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Coolant supply port</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">EGR coolant inlet coupling</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Slide EGR coolant inlet coupling toward the front of the engine on coolant supply port up to
                the face of the oil cooler cover.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">To lock, rotate the coupling either way until single index mark (if visible) or recess no
                longer aligns with index feature on oil cooler cover.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Attempt to slide EGR coolant inlet coupling off coolant supply port to verify locked
                position.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
